{
  "text": "The feeding value [CITATION_1] of SBH relative to corn was also calculated for each concentration of SBH using feed efficiency. The difference between each SBH concentration and the 0% treatment were calculated, divided by the feed efficiency of the 0% SBH, divided by the decimal percentage of concentration of SBH, and multiplied by 100 to get a feeding value of SBH relative to corn for each SBH concentration.",
  "citation_candidates": [
